Anita Sharp-Bolster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anita_Sharp-Bolster 0 Anita Sharp-Bolster (28 August 1895 – 1 June 1985) was an Irish-born American actress who appeared in 88 films and 12 TV series from 1928 to 1978. She was sometimes billed as Anita Bolster. Anita_Sharp-Bolster ( 28_August_1895 – 1_June_1985 ) was an_Irish-born_American_actress who appeared in 88_films and 12_TV_series from 1928 to 1978 .
